install the node package:
    npm install

install the database server:
    1. create a postgresql database 'btc' listening on 127.0.0.1. Run the sql/create_db.sql script on that database.
    2. to run the emails, you will need to export credentials:
        $export EMAIL="emailhere@gmail.com"
        $export PASS="passwordhere"
    3. run it:
        $ npm start
       or, alternatively, run it generating random btc values from 1 to 10:
        $ npm test